
Islamu (/ ˈɪslɑːm /; [A] Icyarabu: اَلْإِسْلَامُ, romanized: al-'Islām, intumwa ya nyuma kandi ihebuje y'Imana.  Ni ryo dini rya kabiri ku isi rifite abayoboke bagera kuri miliyari 1.8 cyangwa 24.1% by'abatuye isi, bazwi ku izina ry'abayisilamu. Abayisilamu bagize umubare munini w’abaturage mu bihugu 49. [7] Islamu yigisha ko Imana ari imwe, imbabazi, ishobora byose, kandi idasanzwe, [8] kandi yayoboye ikiremwamuntu binyuze mu bahanuzi, ibyanditswe byera, n'ibimenyetso bisanzwe.  Ibyanditswe byambere bya Islamu ni Korowani, ikekwa ko ari ijambo ryamagambo yImana, hamwe ninyigisho n'ibikorwa (bita suna, bigizwe na konti bita Hadithi) bya Muhamadi (nko mu 570 - 632 IC). 

Abayisilamu bemeza ko Islamu ari verisiyo yuzuye kandi ikwiye hose ku kwizera kwa mbere guhishurwa inshuro nyinshi mbere binyuze mu bahanuzi, barimo Adamu, Aburahamu, Mose, na Yesu. [11] Abayisilamu bafata Qor'ani mucyarabu ko ari ihishurwa ry’Imana ridahindutse kandi rya nyuma. Kimwe n'andi madini ya Aburahamu, Islamu nayo yigisha urubanza rwa nyuma hamwe n'intungane zahawe ibihembo muri paradizo naho abakiranirwa bahanwa ikuzimu. Ibikorwa by’amadini birimo Inkingi eshanu z’ubuyisilamu, ibyo bikaba ari ibikorwa byo gusenga, ndetse no gukurikiza amategeko ya kisilamu (shariya), akora ku bintu hafi ya byose by’ubuzima na sosiyete, uhereye ku mabanki n’imibereho myiza kugeza ku bagore ndetse n’ibidukikije. [15] Imijyi ya Maka, Madina na Yeruzalemu niho hatuwe ahantu hatagatifu h’ubuyisilamu.
